dct_description_sm: Shows eastern, central, and western drainage areas in southern Indiana, the southern limit of the ice front after Leverett, and geological cross-sections in several locations. Plate VIX. Detached from: A geologic and topographic section across southern Indiana / John Flesher Newsom. In Indiana Department of Geology and Natural Resources twenty-sixth annual report ... 1901. Indianapolis : Wm. B. Burford, 1902. Page 288.
Imprint: Indianapolis, Ind. : Wm. B. Burford, Lith., [1902]
Dimensions: on sheet 22 x 26 cm; Scale: Approximately 1:1,267,200. 1 inch = 20 miles
dct_publisher_sm: Indiana. Department of Geology and Natural Resources
